"      Ticlid (AE, AR, BB, BE, BH, BM, BO, BR, BS, BZ, CN, CO, CR, CY, CZ, DO, EC, EG, FR, GB, GR, GT, GY, HK, HN, HU, IQ, IR, JM, JO, KW, LB, LU, LY, MX, MY, NI, NL, NO, OM, PA, PE, PK, PL, PR, PY, QA, SA, SE, SR, SV, SY, TH, TR, TT, TW, UY, VE, YE);",
